    <h2>Download the Code!</h2>
    <p class="tutP">Now that all the hardware is set up all you have to do is download the code. To do this you just need to run this command in your Terminal:</p>
    <p class="tutP">git clone https://github.com/RobertPuls/drumback.git</p>
    <p class="tutP">Next you'll need to cd into the directory with the downloaded code and run this last command in Terminal:</p>
    <p class="tutP">npm start</p>
    <h2>Ready to go</h2>
    <p class="tutP">Now you're ready to sign up for BeatBot. To signup you'll need your Raspberry Pi IP Address. To get this you can run ifconfig in the Pi's Terminal. You want the address next to inet under the 0wlan section.</p>
